<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.908.46613>
    bibo:endPage "30" ;
    bibo:journal "ZooKeys" ;
    bibo:startPage "19" ;
    bibo:volume "908" ;
    dc:creator "Takano, Tsuyoshi; Kimura, Shoichi; Kano, Yasunori" ;
    dc:date "2020" ;
    dc:title "Host identification for the deep-sea snail genus Haliella with description of a new species (Caenogastropoda, Eulimidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.908.46613.figures1-3>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.908.46613.figures4-5> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.908.46613.figures1-3>
    dc:description "Figures 1 - 3. Holotype of Haliella seisuimaruae sp. nov. and its host sea urchin Brissopsis sp. cf. luzonica (both NSMT-Mo 79088). 1 Photograph of living holotype, attaching to latero-dorsal surface of sea urchin test 2 dorsal or aboral view of same host specimen 3 holotype, apertural and lateral views. Scale bars: 10 mm (2); 2 mm (3)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/376112" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.908.46613.figures4-5>
    dc:description "Figures 4, 5. Paratypes of Haliella seisuimaruae sp. nov., apertural and lateral views. 4 Paratype 1 (MPM Coll. No. 21596) 5 paratype 2 (AORI YK 1520). Scale bar: 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/376113" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

